  <ul><li><a href="2807.html" name="LOC_P39_4783">2807.503 Policy </a></li></ul></ul><hr size="2" width="80%" noshade><!-- TRANSIT - TEXTBAR --><p><b>PART 2807</b> <b><br>
ACQUISITION PLANNING</b> </p>

